{
  "stem": "18654.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 23.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But it-- I was lucky, in a way, because I thought she was going to appear at the wedding and cause problems.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But she was put-- she had to go back to the mental home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "So she wasn't at my wedding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I don't think I'd realized that she was mental, although-- well, I didn't have experience of mental illnesses until then.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Although apparently she'd been in and out of mental homes for some years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know about this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I was only-- don't forget I was only with her for about a year and a half.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But she behaved very strangely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, she did things that-- that you wouldn't do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I questioned it, she said, she was making an experiment, conducting an experiment which would help all the children in England.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was experimenting on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean she didn't hit me or anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm not-- please don't think that-- just mentally disturbed me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I became very frightened of her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I used to try and avoid seeing her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think they knew about it, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think I-- I don't think I reported it, no.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In any case, in those days, you know, anybody who would take a child, they gave them a child, because it saved their life, you know?",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how-- I think they must have-- I imagine that in synagogue they would say, is there anyone willing to take a child.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because you know, England was one of the few countries in the-- in the world that took children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think they took 30,000, or is it-- I'm not quite sure of my facts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took an enormous amount of young children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "America didn't want to know really, only on quota.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
